&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;As inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es se encerram em 1&amp;deg; de mar&amp;ccedil;o e podem ser aqui feitas &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/applicationform/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;Para mais informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre o programa, acesse a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/santandersummerinstitute/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;p&amp;aacute;gina do instituto&lt;/a&gt;e dos &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;cursos dispon&amp;iacute;veis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;A Universidade de Exeter estar&amp;aacute; oferecendo onze cursos de ver&amp;atilde;o com dura&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de quatro semanas para 05 estudantes brasileiros ou colombianos, como parte dos programas internacionais de ver&amp;atilde;o 2016.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;O instituto de ver&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; totalmente financiado pelo Santander Universidades, cujas bolsas de estudo cobrir&amp;atilde;o taxas escolares, alojamento, a maioria das refei&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e taxas de programas sociais. Os selecionados precisar&amp;atilde;o arcar com passagens a&amp;eacute;reas, almo&amp;ccedil;os e outros itens pessoais.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;As inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es se encerram em 1&amp;deg; de mar&amp;ccedil;o e podem ser aqui feitas &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/applicationform/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: body-font; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #373737; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23.4px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;Para mais informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre o programa, acesse a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/santandersummerinstitute/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;p&amp;aacute;gina do instituto&lt;/a&gt;e dos &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.exeter.ac.uk/international/summerschool/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;cursos dispon&amp;iacute;veis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
