	<entry>
		<title>Escola de Verão da Universidade Bauhaus / Alemanha</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://reinter2.furg.br/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9&amp;catid=24&amp;Itemid=137"/>
		<published>2016-03-22T20:52:42-03:00</published>
		<updated>2016-03-22T20:52:42-03:00</updated>
		<id>https://reinter2.furg.br/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9&amp;catid=24&amp;Itemid=137</id>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;A &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/home/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;Universidade Bauhaus&lt;/a&gt;, localizada na cidade de Weimar (Alemanha), est&amp;aacute; com inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es abertas para a &lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Escola&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;de Ver&amp;atilde;o &lt;/strong&gt;que vai acontecer entre os dias &lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;7 de agosto e 2 de setembro de 2016&lt;/strong&gt;. Ser&amp;atilde;o oferecidos cursos em v&amp;aacute;rias &amp;aacute;reas do conhecimento e cursos para o aperfei&amp;ccedil;oamento de l&amp;iacute;nguas estrangeiras.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Os interessados podem consultar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es a respeito do &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/courses/overview/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;conte&amp;uacute;do do curso&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/housing/overview/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;taxas de acomoda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &lt;/a&gt;e outras informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para se candidatar no &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;site da Universidade&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;O prazo final de candidatura &amp;eacute; diferente para cada tipo de curso, variando entre&lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;1 de Maio e 15 de Junho,&lt;/strong&gt;portanto, o candidato deve acessar o site da Universidade para conferir o prazo de inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do curso desejado.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;A &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/home/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;Universidade Bauhaus&lt;/a&gt;, localizada na cidade de Weimar (Alemanha), est&amp;aacute; com inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es abertas para a &lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Escola&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;de Ver&amp;atilde;o &lt;/strong&gt;que vai acontecer entre os dias &lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;7 de agosto e 2 de setembro de 2016&lt;/strong&gt;. Ser&amp;atilde;o oferecidos cursos em v&amp;aacute;rias &amp;aacute;reas do conhecimento e cursos para o aperfei&amp;ccedil;oamento de l&amp;iacute;nguas estrangeiras.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Os interessados podem consultar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es a respeito do &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/courses/overview/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;conte&amp;uacute;do do curso&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en/housing/overview/&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;taxas de acomoda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &lt;/a&gt;e outras informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para se candidatar no &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uni-weimar.de/summerschool/en&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b70e0c; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;site da Universidade&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.625em; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;O prazo final de candidatura &amp;eacute; diferente para cada tipo de curso, variando entre&lt;strong style=&quot;border: 0px none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.4px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;1 de Maio e 15 de Junho,&lt;/strong&gt;portanto, o candidato deve acessar o site da Universidade para conferir o prazo de inscri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do curso desejado.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
